## References & Framework
This risk register follows **NIST SP 800-30** (Risk Assessment) and **NIST IR 8286** (Enterprise Risk Management) frameworks, adapted for hardware product development based on industry best practices from Product Realization Group (PRG) "10 Best Practices for Managing Hardware Development Risk."

